title: Manzod With Children S01E02 The Flying Manzos WEB-DL x264-RKSTR
description: Caroline and Al deal with the disruption of their sons, who turn out to be slobs, moving back into the house. In the midst of the chaos that is her full house, Caroline finds herself concerned about her weight and struggles to exercise. In order to get their mom feeling more confident about tackling her fears, Albie, Chris and Lauren convince Caroline to take a trapeze lesson.
